        <h1 style="font-size: var(--fs-4xl);">Valentine Cave: an easy walk into a lava tube.</h1>
        <p class="lede">
          Of all the caves open to the public at Lava Beds National Monument,
          Valentine is the one I'd hand a first-timer. It's flat, it's well
          preserved, and it's long enough to actually feel the dark.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="container">
        <figure class="article-hero">
